s with tapestry-covered\nseats. AT\nTHE NATIONAL\nSEVENTH AND H STREETS\nFree\nParking\nAltman\u2019s\nLot,\n\u201cEye\u201d\nStrut, I\nBat. 6th\nIth\nTdlrpAen* REpubtie 1234\nRegular $15.95 Lounge Chair, tapestry covered. \u2022\u2022\u25a058.95\nRegular $5.95 Occasional Chair, tapestry covered $3.95\nRegular $9.95 Modern Occasional Table glass top. $4.95\nRegular $19.95 Colonial Desk, walnut finish $13.95\nRegular $1.49 Metal Smoker 79c\nRegular $1.79 End Table walnut finish 98c\nRegular $6.95 Modern Glass Top Coffee Table 95\nRegular $4.95 Drop-Leaf Kitchen Table, unfinished. $2.98\nRegular 98c Kitchen Chair, unfinished 69c\nRegular $4.75 Metal Utility Cabinet. ......T..... $2.98\nRegular $7.95 Enamel Porcelain-Top Table $4.49\nRegular $29.95 15-Pc Wear-Ever Aluminum 5et.. 519.95\nReg. $29.95 Kitchen Cabinet, golden enamel finish, $19.95\nRegular $5.95 Metal Wardrobe $3.98\nRegular $22.95 Chifforobe, nicely finished $14.95\nRegular $6.95 Simmons Metal Bed, walnut finish. $3.98\nRegular $18.95 Folding Cot and Mattress ],95\nRegular $18.95 Desk-Chest, walnut finish $13.95\nRegular $10.95 Chest of Drawers, nicely finished $6.95\nRegular $15.95 Dresser, nicely finished $11.95\nRegular $7.95 Coal Heater, complete with pipe. $4.98\nRegular $19.95 Coal Circulating Heating... $14.95\nRegular $20.75 Oil Circulating Heater.... $16.95\nRegular $15.95 3-Burner Gas Cooker, with Oven. $10.95\nRegular $39.95 Table-Top Gas Range, with Oven $27.95\nRegular $32.95 Coal Range and Warmer $26.95\nRegular $4.98 Oil Heater, economical and handy... $3.95\nBeautiful All Wool Velvet Rugs, 9x12 and 8.3x10.6. Values (FT J QA\nup to $34.75 for\nGuaranteed Felt Base Rugs, 9x12. Sell for $7.95 regularly. 4 Qg-\nPatterns for any room. From J\nCarolina Craft Rag Rugs, 27x36. You\u2019ll want at least 3 or (pl\n4 of them. Sold for $1.89. Special .VU\nAll Wool Axmlnster Scatter Rugs, 27x48 (they are beautiful, Fi Qp\ntoo). Sold for $3.50. Special $1.70\nRubber Door Mats (various colors) 15x25. Value $1.29. Guar-\n$1.69 Oval Hook Rugs. Size 24x48. Choice of qq\n7\nFroo\nDelivery\nto\nMaryland\nand\nVirginia","height":"25905","width":"20458"}}
